  "technicalDetails": "<p>Features:</p><ul><li>Listen for Tag Change</li><li>Listen for Attribute Change</li><li>Listen for Attribute List Changes</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Code Modules:</p><ul><li> ForgeTasks (Runtime)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Number of Blueprint Nodes: 3</p><p>Number of C&#43;&#43; Classes: 4</p><p>Network Replicated: Yes</p><p>Supported Development Platforms: Windows &amp; Linux</p><p>Supported Target Build Platforms: Windows &amp; Linux</p><p>Documentation: <a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/10OVPHxqqwZXDBdwXK5v7adTVtzHGAx5g7wx5ijcpgd4/edit?usp&#61;sharing\" rel=\"nofollow\">Link</a></p><p>Discord: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/vzBsNEH3KH\" rel=\"nofollow\">Link</a></p><p>Example Project: WIP</p><p>Important/Additional Notes: This project only has 3 Blueprint Nodes. I am working on expanding this plugin to numerous more nodes.</p>",
